WEBVTT

00:05:29.092 --> 00:05:32.103
they did send help,
they sent the police to his home,

00:05:32.127 --> 00:05:35.413
and they found him with an arsenal
of loaded weapons

00:05:35.437 --> 00:05:39.399
and on record as being
in possession of a human foot.

00:05:40.260 --> 00:05:42.998
Now, active rescues
are less than one percent

00:05:43.022 --> 00:05:44.895
of our conversations.

00:05:44.919 --> 00:05:47.887
But still, that's about 26 a day.

00:05:47.911 --> 00:05:52.682
And six of those a week are for homicide.

00:05:52.706 --> 00:05:54.506
Typically school shooters.

00:05:54.530 --> 00:05:58.395
We have now completed
more than 32,000 active rescues.

00:05:58.419 --> 00:06:00.649
Our own data and external studies